snippet.title: AAA Clock 2 | Announcement Trailer | Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
In a world where most clocks are either boring or colorless, AAA Clock 2 is going to change everything. This autumn AAA Clock will prove once again that sequels can be just as extraordinary as the originals.
